the algorithms, subsystems/sensor components, monitors and warning systems will continue to be refined and
improved. Verify and validate performance and refine component and subsystem capability as required.

Continue to build Human Systems Integration core/cadre to address Air Wing of the Future (AWOTF). Optimize
work/crew station design to maximize cognitive performance/decision making to support integrated manned
and unmanned teaming (MUM-T) Air Wing of the Future. Engage early with programs during the advanced

