testing and planning activities. Support Large Surface Combatant Naval Energy Storage System project to
transition lessons learned to Energy Magazine and DDG(X). Evaluate and, as applicable, incorporate lessons
learned from the performance of the Energy Magazine-Prototype (EM-P) in EM design and EM technical
deliverables.

Continue development of an Advanced Power Conversion Module (APCM). Perform M&S activities to validate
