Title: Electrostatic Discharge Technical Information Analysis System (ESD TIAS)                                            0.000       0.500       0.500      0.000       0.500
                                                                                                           Articles:          -           -           -          -           -
FY 2025 Plans:
Develop the Electrostatic Discharge Technical Information Analysis System (ESD TIAS) a platform for ESD
information, data, and operational guidance to be disseminated to the fleet for operational safety and acquisition
processes.
FY 2026 Base Plans:
Replace inflexible fixed ESD and OES test criteria with tools, methods, and techniques allowing rapid, effective
design, test and evaluation of ordnance, ordnance surface envelope, enclosures for packaging ordnance,
components, and dielectric isolation.
