D. Acquisition Strategy
In FY 2026, the program will close out the ARV-30 prototyping efforts with GDLS and Textron.

In FY 2026, the program advances to the Engineering and Manufacturing Development (EMD) Phase with two vendors, consisting of the design and manufacturing of
(6) ARV-C4UAS, (6) ARV-30, and (4) ARV-LOG PRTVs for a total of (16) PRTVs per vendor. Total quantity of PRTVs for (2) vendors is (32). The program will also
procure sub-systems such as ballistic hulls, armor coupons, system integration labs, etc.




