A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
Family of Expeditionary Fuel Systems (FEFS) is a line that contains highly versatile fuel systems in support of Fleet Marine Force (FMF) operations. The family contains
individual Table of Allowance Material Control Numbers which support FMF and Marine Air-Ground Task Force (MAGTF) operations and future operating concepts by
providing all aspects of land and littoral-based fuel support to include receiving, test, additization, storage, sensors and metering, transfer and dispensing of fuel.

