Description: This program supports development, testing and evaluation of technologies and commercial
systems that will provide needed capabilities to EOD and Expeditionary forces in responding to the wide range

B. Accomplishments/Planned Programs ($ in Millions, Article Quantities in Each)                                                               FY 2026   FY 2026     FY 2026
