- AN/SPY-6(V)3 (Ford CVN)
- AN/SPY-6(V)4 (DDG 51 Flight IIA destroyer backfit)

 AN/SPY-6(V)1 provides multi-mission capabilities, supporting long range ballistic missile detection, tracking and discrimination, plus Area and Self Defense against air/
